org.pure4j.collections

Class PersistentTreeMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pure4j.collections.APersistentMap<K,V>
      • org.pure4j.collections.PersistentTreeMap<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable<Map.Entry<K,V>>, Map<K,V>, Counted, IMapIterable<K,V>, IPersistentMap<K,V>, Reversible<Map.Entry<K,V>>, Seqable<Map.Entry<K,V>>, Sorted<K,Map.Entry<K,V>>

    public class PersistentTreeMap<K,V>
extends APersistentMap<K,V>
implements Reversible<Map.Entry<K,V>>, Sorted<K,Map.Entry<K,V>>
    Persistent Red Black Tree Note that instances of this class are constant values i.e. add/remove etc return new values

    See Okasaki, Kahrs, Larsen et al
